ty and\/or additional services you may need. You can contact the department for more information on this <a href=\"http:\/\/www.immigrationlanka.com\/contact-6-6.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here<\/a>.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Good to know:<\/strong> Alternatively, fill in the form when you are at the Department of Immigration.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"how to get visa sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"how to get visa sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-34246 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114054\/how-to-get-visa-sri-lanka-450x300.jpg 450w, 