ner\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\">online via the form<\/a> and got approved within a few days. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Always follow the guidelines, double or triple check your details when you&#x2019;re filling out the forms, and make sure your passport is up to date and valid for at least 6 months upon entering Sri Lanka.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy this beautiful country and everything it has to offer! <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><small><strong>Disclaimer: <\/strong><em>This article is updated regularly but the visa situation might change. Please always double-check with the local authorities. <\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Which visa for Sri Lanka is for you? The good news is that getting a tourist visa for Sri Lanka is relatively simple and can be booked ahead online as an electronic visa (ETA). This can either be done by yourself or a third party. It is easiest to use an online booking service for [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":34248,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"visa sri lanka","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"9905,11103,19196,644,11331,22193"},"categories":[5245,75,9],"tags":[6446],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Visa Sri Lanka: How to get it and Entry Requ